<div id="review_15328196" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/15328196" />
    <a title="Spencer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/904824-spencer"><img alt="Spencer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1202924044p2/904824.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/15328196?book_show_action=true">Feb 13, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Spencer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Spencer" href="/user/show/904824-spencer">Spencer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/904824-spencer?shelf=faith-and-religion">faith-and-religion</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer15328196" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8659527452676125987">I am re-reading this book again because I think it is one of the best ever written concerning the Book of Mormon. Though it is not a &quot;commentary&quot; on the Book or Mormon, it provides the reader with a different perspective on how to approach it. With Elder Holland&apos;s insights compounded with a powerful testimony, it is one that stands out on my bookshelf and I&apos;d recommend it to anyone.</span>
  <span id="freeText8659527452676125987" style="display:none">I am re-reading this book again because I think it is one of the best ever written concerning the Book of Mormon. Though it is not a "commentary" on the Book or Mormon, it provides the reader with a different perspective on how to approach it. With Elder Holland's insights compounded with a powerful testimony, it is one that stands out on my bookshelf and I'd recommend it to anyone.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8659527452676125987" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
